org.pragmaticminds.crunch.api.holder

Class Holder<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pragmaticminds.crunch.api.holder.Holder<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Deprecated. 
    Part of the old API

    @Deprecated
public class Holder<T>
extends Object
implements Serializable
    This class is the basis for all holders (for all primitives / DataType. Holders "hold" their Value to pass it into the Evaluation Function (Pattern.

    This class is Serializable but does not serialize it's current Value! This is not necessary as it always "resettet" during the Evaluation.
